%%{init: {"sequence": {"mirrorActors": false}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    actor UserA as User A
    actor UserB as User B
    participant UI as Task Detail / Chat
    participant API as Next.js API Routes
    participant DB as Supabase Database

    UserA->>UI: Open Chat view
    UI->>API: GET /api/messages?projectId
    API->>DB: Fetch messages
    DB-->>API: Messages[]
    API-->>UI: Render messages

    UserA->>UI: Type & send message
    UI->>UI: Optimistic update
    UI->>API: POST /api/messages {projectId, content, userId}
    API->>DB: INSERT message
    API-->>UI: New message
    UI->>API: GET /api/messages (re-fetch)

    UserA->>UI: Open Task Detail
    UserA->>UI: Write comment
    UI->>API: POST /api/comments {taskId, userId, content}
    API->>DB: INSERT comment
    API-->>UI: Comment added

    UserA->>UI: Edit task status
    UI->>API: PATCH /api/tasks {id, status, ...updates}
    API->>DB: UPDATE task
    API-->>UI: Updated task

    UserA->>UI: Start Video Call
    UI->>API: GET /api/meeting?projectId
    API->>DB: Fetch project meeting URL
    DB-->>API: URL
    API-->>UI: meetingUrl
    UI->>UI: Open Google Meet / meetingUrl in new tab
    UserB->>UI: Start Video Call
    UI->>UI: Open same Google Meet link
